    - Stuns - User your Level 4 Stun, the resist rate is about the same and its a 1 sec cast time.  <br>
    - Root - If your MA has a hard time getting agro, Root is great.  Just make sure the MA knows to step into the mobs as root will cause agro to the closest player.<br>
